WorkItem.Description:
The ComboBox controls allows the user to input the text (e.g. first characters) of the list item it should select.

The DataGridComboBoxColumn doesn't support this feature when the cell is not in edit mode.

I belive you just need to extend the OnInput method with:

// Text input will start the edit mode
if (e is TextCompositionEventArgs)
{
    BeginEdit(e);
}
